opencli browser ankiweb fill 10 "ai reading language chatgpt openai"
opencli browser ankiweb fill 11 "https://github.com/stors789/Daily-AI-Reading-Reinforcement/issues"
opencli browser ankiweb eval 'document.querySelectorAll("input[maxlength=\\"9\\"]")[1].value = "";'
opencli browser ankiweb fill 17 "<b>Daily AI Reading Reinforcement (AI 每日阅读强化)</b><br><br>[EN] Bridges the gap between rote memorization and practical language application. It automatically extracts the vocabulary or flashcards you've studied today and leverages AI to generate a short, engaging reading passage incorporating those exact terms.<br><br>[ZH] 跨越死记硬背与实际语言应用之间的鸿沟。它能自动提取您今天学习过的词汇或卡片，利用 AI 自动生成一篇包含这些词汇的短文供您阅读，在语境中自然强化记忆。<br><br>[JA] 暗記と実際の言語応用のギャップを埋めるアドオンです。今日学習した単語やカードを自動的に抽出し、AIを活用してそれらの用語を自然に組み込んだ短い読解文章を生成します。<br><br>---<br><b>Key Features / 核心功能 / 主な機能:</b><ul><li><b>Contextual Reinforcement (语境强化 / 文脈での強化)</b>: See your newly learned vocabulary in a natural context.</li><li><b>Tailored to Your Progress (为您量身定制 / 進捗に合わせた内容)</b>: Extracts new cards and failed review cards that you studied <i>today</i>.</li><li><b>Customizable Prompts (自定义提示词 / カスタマイズ可能なプロンプト)</b>: Dictate the language, difficulty level, and formatting for the generated articles.</li><li><b>Multi-Language Support (多语言支持 / 多言語サポート)</b>: Compact UI optimized for English, Chinese, and Japanese.</li><li><b>Closed-Loop Learning (闭环学习 / 学習のループ)</b>: Seamlessly save the AI-generated articles back into Anki as new reading cards.</li><li><b>Flexible AI Integration (灵活的 AI 接口 / 柔軟なAI統合)</b>: Works perfectly with any OpenAI-compatible API provider (OpenAI, DeepSeek, etc.).</li></ul>---<br><b>How to use / 如何使用 / 使い方:</b><ol><li>Install the add-on and restart Anki. / 安装插件并重启 Anki。</li><li>Go to the add-on settings to set up your API Key and Base URL. / 进入插件设置，配置您的 API Key 和 Base URL。</li><li>Click on the <i>'AI Reading Reinforcement'</i> menu entry. / 点击菜单栏的 AI 强化阅读入口。</li><li>Select the decks you studied today, choose the specific fields to send to the AI, and click Generate! / 选择今天学习过的牌组，勾选需要发送给 AI 的字段，然后点击生成！</li></ol><br><i>Note: This add-on requires you to bring your own OpenAI-compatible API key. / 注意：本插件需要您自己提供兼容 OpenAI 格式的 API 密钥。</i>"
